exec-explain
SELECT (a, (b, 'a'), (c, 'b', 5)) = (9, (a+c, s), (5, s, a)) FROM t.t
----
render     0  render  ·         ·                                                                                      (column8)                          ·
 │         0  ·       render 0  (((((a = 9) AND (b = (a + c))) AND (s = 'a')) AND (c = 5)) AND (s = 'b')) AND (a = 5)  ·                                  ·
 └── scan  1  scan    ·         ·                                                                                      (a, b, c, d, j, s, rowid[hidden])  ·
·          1  ·       table     t@primary                                                                              ·                                  ·
·          1  ·       spans     ALL                                                                                    ·                                  ·

